MailerSoft,is,an,email,marketing,service,that,provides,effective,and,easy,to,use,tools,for,marketing,professionals,The,service,enables,marketers,to,launch,successful,email,marketing,campaigns,by,offering,custom,designed,newsletters,subscriber,management,tools,reliable,servers,and,detailed,newsletter,reports,MailerSoft,offers,a,REST,API,for,programmatic,access,to,MailerSoft,services,Example,API,methods,include,Campaigns,Lists,and,Subscribers,All,responses,are,in,JSON,format,and,an,API,key,is,required